  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effectiveness of physiotherapy program in the treatment of cluster
      headaches. Half of participants will receive a program of physiotherapy and usual drugs,
      while the other will receive an exercise program and usual drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Previous studies have shown positive effects of physical therapy in patients with primary
      headache.

      However, so far no study that assessed the effect of a physiotherapy program combined with
      regular medication in patients with cluster headache.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
